			<div class="content" id="post-content-1722342">
									

<p>I think the timeline could use some clarification.</p>
<p>Here's what I'm seeing:<br />
13 yrs old: William discovers Malo via Sara<br />
plus 4 days : They freak out<br />
?? William moves out for college<br />
2 ys ago : Sara commits suicide</p>
<p>Namely, I'm thinking that app stores and such are a bit too recent for him to be contemporary with them at 13 unless he's headed for college at 15<br />
(and Sara didn't long outlive the freakout).<br />
2013 -4/5 years for him to reach 17/18 (since if Sara had died before he moved out, he'd have mentioned it), - 2 years for present day gets us 2007-2006. When was the first App Store?</p>
<p>Also, where's the Foundation in all this?</p>
<p>EDIT:Oops, accidentally plus sized that &quot;4 days&quot;.</p>

