			<div class="content" id="post-content-1722351">
									

<p>I found that kinda funny. As if to say &quot;in four days, THEY GO APE-SHIT!!!&quot;</p>
<p>Anyway, my intention was that Sara waited for William to move out before she committed suicide, so here's the general timeline:</p>
<p>13 years old: MalO is downloaded<br />
plus 4 days: &quot;Hi guys!&quot;<br />
18 years: William moves out for college<br />
plus 1-7 days: Sara commits suicide<br />
20 years old: present</p>
<p>e: As for the year, I mentioned that William got his MalO on his crappy flip-phone, so that should cover any time-based errors.</p>
<p>As for the foundation, you could interpret this in many ways, two explanations come to mind off the top of my head:</p>
<p>1) The world already knows about anomalous stuff, like in the broken masquerade cannon, and The Foundation was spending their resources elsewhere.<br />
2) This is how they found MalO, and William is going to a foundation front for therapy.</p>

