														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1722517">
									

<p>Like many first-person pieces here, this suffers from tone consistency problems: the phrase &quot;some bestial abomination&quot; in particular seemed really at odds with the narrator's writing style, and I found the closing sentences a little too histrionic. However, I think there are too few stories showing people carrying on some semblance of normal life after their encounter with the supernatural, and I really like the few glimpses of Capone's behaviour that we do get. +1</p>

